# <type>(<scope>): <subject>      ── max 100 chars, imperative, no trailing period
#
#   type:  feat | fix | docs | chore | test | refactor | perf | build | ci | style | revert
#   scope: subsystem, e.g. canary, tenancy, control, agent, bus, ci
#
# Body (wrap ~72): what changed and why.
#
# Reference the sprint + requirement IDs, e.g.:  [S0]   or   [S7, F2]
#
# Footer (optional):
#   BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
#   Closes #<issue>
#
# Enable this template once with:
#   git config commit.template .gitmessage
